  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/40cfe0dbe8f7d02e3e0290e6f4fb0b50.poster.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/40cfe0dbe8f7d02e3e0290e6f4fb0b50.webm?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/40cfe0dbe8f7d02e3e0290e6f4fb0b50.mp4?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>Ragdoll Training Center is a physics based arcade game where you push a ragdoll character through the map.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of challenging maps with different levels of difficulty.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoid obstacles and reach the finish in shortest possible time.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compete for thousandths of a second differences with other players in global ranking.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create your own maps in built-in Map Editor and try maps made by other players.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game is also available for Android and iOS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/4ef6af3d469965840a8baa6714e6cefa.poster.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/4ef6af3d469965840a8baa6714e6cefa.webm?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/4ef6af3d469965840a8baa6714e6cefa.mp4?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/86c1cae5ac5cfe2a2e2a7bb053087582.poster.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/86c1cae5ac5cfe2a2e2a7bb053087582.webm?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/86c1cae5ac5cfe2a2e2a7bb053087582.mp4?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/1005e9c7cad60467a60ef2d1baea3b7e.poster.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/1005e9c7cad60467a60ef2d1baea3b7e.webm?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/1005e9c7cad60467a60ef2d1baea3b7e.mp4?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't worry about hurting the ragdoll - it's a professional, ready to retry again and again... and again!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/60ab9f19ef97a03717302e299c0cd85e.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/40cfe0dbe8f7d02e3e0290e6f4fb0b50.poster.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/40cfe0dbe8f7d02e3e0290e6f4fb0b50.webm?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/40cfe0dbe8f7d02e3e0290e6f4fb0b50.mp4?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>Ragdoll Training Center is a physics based arcade game where you push a ragdoll character through the map.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of challenging maps with different levels of difficulty.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoid obstacles and reach the finish in shortest possible time.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compete for thousandths of a second differences with other players in global ranking.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create your own maps in built-in Map Editor and try maps made by other players.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game is also available for Android and iOS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/4ef6af3d469965840a8baa6714e6cefa.poster.avif?t=1734740877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127610/extras/4ef6af3d469965840a8baa6714e6cefa.webm?t=1734740877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor